                    "body": "This is very annoying. Experienced it myself. Wrote a Unit-Test, but have no idea which would be the best way to fix it. Hoping for some feedback on github.\r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/github.com\/zendframework\/zf2\/pull\/2386",
